OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSurgeon claims hospital    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F'covered up' patient       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fblinding                   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A surgeon sacked by a hospital after   
OL,6, raising safety concerns has accused the
OL,7, trust of a cover-up after a patient was
OL,8, partially blinded during an operation. 
OL,10,FJuanita Graham, 41, lost the sight in  
OL,11,Fher left eye during an operation at    
OL,12,FBath's Royal United Hospital (RUH) in  
OL,13,F2019. She is now suing the trust.      
OL,15,FSerryth Colbert said he was put down as
OL,16,Fthe lead author on an investigation    
OL,17,Finto the incident, but said he "did not
OL,18,Fwrite a word" of it.                   
OL,20,FThe RUH has declined to comment.       
